text: Yeah man, first year memories - group pe jab pics share hui I started remembering some of the times, our Delhi-Ghaziabad-Meerut trip and Antaragni. Those were fun times. I am sure you'll excel too in whatever you do. Cheers! PS: Me bhi Spotify pe tera Friend activity dekhta hu :)
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar

text: Case when? Mile toh I think bohot pehle hi the but acche se final year me hi jaane and I realized that you are a person who gets what he sets as his goal no matter what and I really admire that. I loved the conversations we had in Goa and Goa ke adventures toh xD Anyway mil toh apan rahe hi hai (hopefully this year). Aur apni beard ke baal nochna bandh kar :)
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar

text: Hey man! We haven't talked a lot, but whenever we did I always felt like an immediate connection. Some topics that I have rarely found anyone to relate with, I could relate with you and one of them was New York City of course! Apni ek US road trip pending rahi boss! That Bryan Adams concert I'll remember for a long time to come, it was so much fun vibing to all those songs. Hope we meet soon and all the best! And if the band you're in starts playing different tunes I'll see you on the dark side of the moon :D
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar

text: Pehli mulaakat was jab me Quora pe GoT ka kuch answer de raha tha, fir realize hua oh yeh toh mere wing me hai xD. Hopefully the future holds another project for us jaha firse saath kaam karenge :) Tandon aur Doc ke saath Offline, sutte ki treat aur Goa - yahi baate toh aage yaad aayengi xD.
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar

PS: CoD aa jaa, pew pew

text: I always remembered you as divtrip in my head xD. Pehle hall me mile the fir NYO and then MClub. Kaafi maza aayi thi tumse NYO me baat karke. Aisa lagta tha ki you are a man of few but powerful words xD Hope to stay in touch. All the best!
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar

text:
Hello!
I was hoping meri yeh waali photo nahi aayegi, but aa hi gayi xD. Yeh memoir likhte hue saari AUV and first year Antaragni ki memories yaad aa gayi. Sahi me bohot baate karte the xD. PHY102 ke marks ke baad ka rona yaad hai? xD Here's to the memories and all the best for the future!

Surat aane se pehle Ahmedabad aa jaata hu me hi xD Baaki 'umbrella organization' toh hai hi apna xD. All the best!

text: Hello! Somehow I still have the nerd image of you in my mind xD I think NYO days were where we started knowing each other and then randomly CCD me toh mil hi jaate the. You have a characteristic handwave while greeting that I'll never forget. Humesha CCD me milte time aise hi wave karta tha xD. I also remember cycling or walking around academic area with you at times, it was fun. All the best!
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar

text:
Pence bhai,

Wo project toh xD for some reason mujhe usme wahi cheez sabse zyada yaad aati hai jab Khare se baithke cameras samjh rahe the apan ek din. Project ke alava bhi Aerial Robotics ko itna aage pohochane ke liye congrats! Aur aise hi aage bhi chaapte raho! All the best, and hope to meet sometime soon :)
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar

text: Hello. We've probably known each other since first year. I think linguistics ke class ke bahar mile the. CCD me random meetings toh hoti hi rehti thi. The most fun memory for me is Bangalore - ekdum wheeeeee karte hue cycle chalayi thi towards the mall xD. I loved the trips we went on as well - holi on your house's rooftop and Udaipur. Here's to the good times! All the best!

text: Kabhi saath me campus wapas aana hua toh sabse pehle DoAA canteen chalenge. Maggi, chai and then tabki life ka critical analysis, uske baad Hall 12 canteen me bahar coffee pe current events ka discussion xD. You barging into my room and hugging everyone always filled me with happiness, those hugs are something I'll miss. I love that I have a friend jiske saath deep discussions bhi kar sakte hai aur random gifs bhi bhej sakte. Like I've been saying since first year, thoda zyada decisive bano, baaki toh sab changa si. Don't forget Wednesday evenings and skipping ropes tod mat dena xD.
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar

text:
Yo bro!
AUV ki first year summer memories yaad aati hai apni toh xD Pool me bot ka testing uske baad wapas hall jaana. Uske alava jab bhi hall me dikhe ho smile karte hue hi mile ho. Waise hi smile karte rehna aage bhi :) All the best!
author: Naishadh Nimesh Parmar
